i slopes, golf courses, hunting spots and five-star hotels. The developer o=
ffered locals a large number of new apartments in town in exchange for thei=
r old homes, creating a village of property tycoons almost overnight.=E2=80=
=9CI was so happy then,=E2=80=9D said Zhao, who was a teenager at the time =
and later inherited the properties.=C2=A0Now, all five of her apartments si=
t empty. Only one of the stores has a tenant. =E2=80=A6The market is facing=
