=C2=A0</em>reason, whether or not you are going to a competitor. But the fi=
rm will, as a matter of informal policy, let you keep that compensation if =
you leave for certain=C2=A0<em>good=C2=A0</em>reasons: if you=E2=80=99ve be=
en there a long time and are retiring, say, or you=E2=80=99re going into pu=
