 style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-w=
idth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgr=
ound-color: #ccc;">immense vogue</a> for a while, but it was always easy to=
 see <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/35147391.2573=
45/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDgtMDEv=
