mprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"colo=
r: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bor=
der-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #c=
cc;">the flaw in the argument</a>. The flaw was: Why would multiplying the =
supply of an arbitrary electronic token by six multiply its total value by =
six? If everyone had one Meaningless Token, and then by operation of a comp=
uter everyone instead has=C2=A0six Meaningless Tokens, how has their <em>ac=
tual wealth=C2=A0</em>increased?</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">With apart=
ments in China the situation is a bit more ambiguous. Here=E2=80=99s a Wall=
