MIC List, they became eligible for inclusion in MSCI indexes at the next re=
view, and they were added into the indexes one to three months after they b=
ecame eligible, despite the risks those companies pose to national security=
.=E2=80=9D Right: When they are on the banned list, they are not in the ind=
